ing_recovered><tutorial_video_msg_1><![CDATA[We're under attack in an outlying sector! Come to our rescue.<br><br><blue>Follow the flashing arrow:</blue> <blue>Left-click</blue> the location to which your ship should fly.<br>Over and out!]]></tutorial_video_msg_1><tutorial_video_msg_3_1><![CDATA[Nice work, space pilot! Remember to repair your ship after being hit by enemy fire.<br><br>To repair it, just press <blue>[3]</blue> or click the <blue>repair bot button in the shortcut bar.</blue><br><br>Note: Robots will stop repairing your ship as soon the ship moves.]]></tutorial_video_msg_3_1><tutorial_video_msg_3_2><![CDATA[Do you see those <blue>glowing orange boxes?</blue> They contain valuable resources.<br><br><blue>Click on them to collect them.</blue><br><br>Find out what's inside them at the top of the screen or in your logbook.]]></tutorial_video_msg_3_2><tutorial_video_msg_4_1><![CDATA[Well done, pilot! Destroy enemies in space to get <blue>money and resources.</blue><br><br>This will increase your <blue>experience and honor points,</blue> allowing you to enter new galaxies and maps.]]></tutorial_video_msg_4_1><tutorial_video_msg_4_2><![CDATA[Escort your ally's damaged ship to the <blue>space station</blue> so that it can be repaired.<br><br><blue>Contact the ship by flying close to it.</blue>]]></tutorial_video_msg_4_2><tutorial_video_msg_5><![CDATA[Thanks for your help! Unfortunately, I lost my cargo. You'll find <blue>3 Prometium, 2 Endurium</blue> and <blue>1 Terbium</blue> not far from here.<br><br>Could you get them for me? Just <blue>click on the items and wait until they've been beamed aboard.</blue>]]></tutorial_video_msg_5><tutorial_video_msg_6><![CDATA[All right, backup is finally here. <br><br><blue>Follow us to the jump portal</blue> so we can fly back to the station and have my ship repaired.]]></tutorial_video_msg_6><tutorial_video_msg_7><![CDATA[This is the <blue>jump portal</blue> that takes you to other maps. <br><br>Press <blue>[J]</blue> or <blue>click on the circle symbol</blue> on the upper right to fly through the gate.]]></tutorial_video_msg_7><tutorial_video_msg_2_1><![CDATA[Quick, destroy the three rival ships! <br><br><blue>Left-click them to target in on the ships.</blue><br><br>Launch your attack with the <blue>[1]</blue> key or the <blue>laser button in the shortcut bar</blue>.]]></tutorial_video_msg_2_1><tutorial_video_msg_2_2><![CDATA[Kill opponents quicker with <blue>rockets</blue>. Fire off rockets with the <blue>[2]</blue> key or the <blue>rocket button in the shortcut bar</blue>.]]></tutorial_video_msg_2_2><log_collected_firework><![CDATA[You received %! %2! fireworks.]]></log_collected_firework><setting_autostart><![CDATA[Log into client automatically]]></setting_autostart><setting_doubleClickAttack><![CDATA[Double-click to launch attack]]></setting_doubleClickAttack><title_cli><![CDATA[Command line interface]]></title_cli><title_repair><![CDATA[Repair]]></title_repair><video_window_header><![CDATA[Incoming message]]></video_window_header><video_btn_continue><![CDATA[Next]]></video_btn_continue><video_btn_showAll><![CDATA[Show all]]></video_btn_showAll><btn_repair><![CDATA[Repair]]></btn_repair><btn_leaveGame><![CDATA[Leave]]></btn_leaveGame><msg_autostart_warning><![CDATA[Use this setting carefully.
When the game is loaded, you will be automatically logged into the client, and other pilots will be able to attack you immediately.]]></msg_autostart_warning><btn_hangar><![CDATA[Hangar]]></btn_hangar><tutorial_video_msg_8_1><![CDATA[Safe at last! You can keep the resources.<br><br><blue>Sell them at the station</blue> by clicking on the <blue>Trade button on the top right.</blue>]]></tutorial_video_msg_8_1><tutorial_video_msg_8_2><![CDATA[Take a look around the <blue>hangar</blue>. You can buy <blue>new ships</blue> and <blue>weapons</blue> there.<br><br>You're on your own from now on, but you're a capable space pilot, and I'm sure you won't have any problems.<br><br>Thanks again, and good luck! Over and out.]]></tutorial_video_msg_8_2><tutorial_video_msg_move><![CDATA[<blue>Left-click</blue> the target coordinates.]]></tutorial_video_msg_move><tutorial_video_msg_wrongdirection><![CDATA[Wrong direction!<br><br><blue>Follow the arrow!</blue>]]></tutorial_video_msg_wrongdirection><tutorial_video_msg_follow><![CDATA[C'mon, move it. We've got to get to the station quickly so I can repair my ship.]]></tutorial_video_msg_follow><title_achievement><![CDATA[Start-up quests]]></title_achievement><title_reward><![CDATA[Reward:]]></title_reward><achievement_header><![CDATA[Did you like this item? Click here to buy a second one for a special price!]]></achievement_header><achievement_FIRST_FLY_header><![CDATA[Explorer quest]]></achievement_FIRST_FLY_header><achievement_FIRST_FLY_directive><![CDATA[Explore your base and win a new ship!]]></achievement_FIRST_FLY_directive><achievement_FIRST_FLY_reward><![CDATA[Liberator Starfighter]]></achievement_FIRST_FLY_reward><achievement_FIRST_FLY_tooltip><![CDATA[Click in the orbit to navigate to a certain point and explore your home base.]]></achievement_FIRST_FLY_tooltip><achievement_FIRST_STREUNER_header><![CDATA[Streuner quest]]></achievement_FIRST_STREUNER_header><achievement_FIRST_STREUNER_directive><![CDATA[Destroy a Streuner.]]></