 operational again.<br>The scout drones are reporting an extra energy signature.<br> The power station must have been linked to their HQ. When we reactivated the power station, it triggered the HQ repair zone.<br>Fly into the zone and repair your ships.]]></transmission_groupgate_relay_station_bypassed><transmission_groupgate_hq_1><![CDATA[Their HQ's running on auxiliary power. They must have interrupted the power supply to turn off life support and keep us out.]]></transmission_groupgate_hq_1><transmission_groupgate_hq_2><![CDATA[Activate the other power stations to increase the power supply.<br>Prepare yourselves: Once the HQ is operational, Century Falcon will know we've penetrated his defenses and attack us.<br>Get ready for the battle of a lifetime!]]></transmission_groupgate_hq_2><transmission_groupgate_hq_fight><![CDATA[Our intel was accurate - the pirates were defending the power stations to prevent us from activating HQ.<br>Find and activate all their power stations!]]></transmission_groupgate_hq_fight><transmission_groupgate_boss_arrival><![CDATA[Top notch! The extra power reactivated the HQ and Century Falcon's come out of hiding to defend it.<br>This is it, destroy Century Falcon and the operation will be complete.]]></transmission_groupgate_boss_arrival><transmission_groupgate_mission_end><![CDATA[Operation Charlie Foxtrot successful!<br>That was some fine flying! You've earned yourselves some downtime.<br>Over and out!]]></transmission_groupgate_mission_end><msg_jump_failed_no_group><![CDATA[You must be part of a group to jump to this map.]]></msg_jump_failed_no_group><msg_jump_failed_no_instance><![CDATA[No instance available]]></msg_jump_failed_no_instance><msg_create_target_instance_map><![CDATA[No instance found - Creating instance for group leader ...]]></msg_create_target_instance_map><msg_jump_to_target_instance_map><![CDATA[Instance found - Beaming players to the instance ...]]></msg_jump_to_target_instance_map><msg_jump_failed_map_full><![CDAT