Thank you for your continued support!]]></gate_billboard_birthday_6><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_01_01><![CDATA[Space Pilot!<br>Glad to see a friendly face - listen I got trapped here and could need <blue>your help!</blue>]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_01_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_01_02><![CDATA[Yeah, before you ask, I really don't know how I ended up in here.<br>Just jumped through that gate that came out of nowhere and here I am ...]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_01_02><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_01_03><![CDATA[... my cargo room is half empty, ship's severely damaged  and most of<br>... wait, what is that?!<br> <blue>Watch out!!</blue>]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_01_03><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_02_01><![CDATA[Well this is more annoying than dangerous but <blue>I think I can help you </blue> - just need a little time setting things up ...]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_02_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_03_01><![CDATA[Well there you are again - thought these Streuners would have driven you off.]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_03_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_03_02><![CDATA[Remember that I lost most of my cargo? Actually I still have limited <blue>control over some boosters</blue> I just bought recently.]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_03_02><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_03_03><![CDATA[Let's see if we can put them to some use. Don't expect and be sure to <blue>stay close to the booster</blue> - and check the <blue>booster interface</blue> in your ship's computer - prepare for another wave of enemies!]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_03_03><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_04_01><![CDATA[OK <blue>activating booster 1.</blue> Now - this should give you some <blue>extra damage</blue> for a brief amount of time. I will send the booster's <blue>coordinates to your navigation system.</blue>]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_04_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_05_01><![CDATA[Worked like a charm, didn't it? I will reroute energy to the <blue>second booster</blue> now, this will increase your <blue>shield regeneration rate.</blue> Stay sharp!]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_05_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_06_01><![CDATA[Hey bud, welcome back! I figured out how to implement a series circuit that activates boosters more rapidly. <blue>Health-regeneration and hitpoints</blue> will be boosted.]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_06_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_07_01><![CDATA[Good you made it back. I've been tinkering around a bit in your absence -  you might need to move to get all the advantages, though. Good Luck.]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_07_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_08_01><![CDATA[You are quite a pilot! I developed some activation patterns, which should help you a lot.]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_08_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_09_01><![CDATA[Damn, these things are starting to scare me. Being trapped in here feels like living in a goldfish bowl! Oh, and here they come again!]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_09_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_10_01><![CDATA[This will be a hard wave ... be sure to use the <blue>boosters,</blue> mate.]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_10_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_11_01><![CDATA[Hey, welcome back! Just wondering if you believe in all these "end of the world" rumors  that have been spreading recently? Oh, here we go again!]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_11_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_12_01><![CDATA[Hi, buddy! Say, don't I know you from somewhere? You seem kind of familiar ... INCOMING!]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_12_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_13_01><![CDATA[Ok ... once again, I've improved the booster activation patterns. Check it out and give me some feedback ... I just might be on to something here!]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_13_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_14_01><![CDATA[What the <blue>frack</blue> is this thing? I'll try to power up the <blue>boosters</blue> as long as I can - make the best out of it. Good Luck!]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_14_01><tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_15_01><![CDATA[My friend, it has been an <blue>honor</blue> fighting with you. I will reroute <blue>all remaining energy</blue> to keep the <blue>boosters</blue> going. Should <blue>life support fail</blue> before you've brought this wave down, please try to <blue>get me out of here.</blue> Farewell.]]></tutorial_video_6thbday_beacon_communication_15_01><q2_condition_REAL_TIME_HASTE><![CDATA[Finish this quest in %TIME%!]]></q2_condition_REAL_TIME_HASTE><ttip_questwin_notacceptable_DATE><![CDATA[This quest will be available in %BEGIN% and lasts %TIME%.]]></ttip_questwin_notacceptable_DATE><ttip_questwin_notacceptable_PRE_QUEST><![CDATA[%MIN% of %MAX% quests have been completed to unlock this quest.]]></ttip_questwin_notacceptable_PRE_QUEST><ttip_setting_quality_high_option_unsupported_gpu><![CDATA[High quality settings not supported - GPU acceleration not available.]]></ttip_setting_quality_high_option_unsupported_gpu><log_msg_gg_completed_bday><![CDATA[Way to go, Pilot! You completed the Birthday Gate.]]></log_msg_gg_completed_bday><msg_station_built_deflector_off><![CDATA[%CLAN% is nowin control of the %STATION% Battle Station on the %MAP% map!
